high_descs: From the living room turn right move forward turn right move towards the dining room turn left move forward turn right again turn left and then turn right move forward turn right towards the diningtable.
Collect the potato from the bowl on the dining table.
Turn around move forward turn left move to fridge
Open the refrigerator, place the potato in the rack and close. Wait sometime again open and take the potato from the refrigerator.
Move forward turn around towards the microwave
Open the microwave, place the potato inside and close.
anns.task_desc: Potato to be baked in the Microwave

high_descs: Go to the diningtable on the left side.
Open the door. Place the potato on the left side on the third level. Close the door. Open the door after ten seconds. Take the potato. Close the door.
Turn around towards the microwave. Open the door. Place the potato on the left side. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Find a potato, cool it and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the diningtable.
Pick up potato from the table.
Head to the fridge door, open the door and put the bread on the shelf.
Open the refrigerator door and take out the bread, close the door.
Take the bread to the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Get the potato from the kitchen table, put it in the refrigerator and then put potato in the microwave
